|-----------------------|---------------------------|---------------------|
| FindServers           | OpenSecureChannel         | CreateSession       |
| GetEndpoints          | CloseSecureChannel        | ActivateSession     |
| RegisterServer        |                           | CloseSession        |
|                       |                           | Cancel              |

