| AddReferences              | BrowseNext                     | QueryNext         | HistoryRead           |                    |
| DeleteNodes                | TranslateBrowsePathsToNodeIds  |                   | Write                 |                    |
| DeleteReferences           | RegisterNodes                  |                   | HistoryUpdate         |                    |
|                            | UnregisterNodes                |                   |                       |                    |

